# Images
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.svg
*.webp
*.ico
*.bmp

# Docs / PDFs (re-enable later by setting ANTHROPIC_API_KEY if you want them in the graph)
*.pdf
*.md
*.mdx
*.txt
*.csv

# Markup/data files classified as "docs" (need LLM key for semantic extraction)
*.html
*.xml
*.yaml
*.yml

# Asset/upload dirs
uploads/
public/
**/assets/
